lead_paragraph: Louisville added a late-night wrinkle to its defense, ran out to a big lead and hung on to earn a trip to the Battle 4 Atlantis championship game.

headline.print_headline: No. 10 Louisville Beats Wichita State 62-52 in Bahamas
